window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b><i>\"I was utterly consumed.\" </i></b>(Rachel Grey,<i> USA Today </i>best-selling author) </p> <p><b>With her heart literally in his hands, Celia will have to try and bargain with a devil. </b></p> <p>Edward Fasbender is my captor. </p> <p>Trapped on this island on which he owns everything - including, it seems, me. </p> <p>He told me he would break me, but I thought he meant in the bedroom. It turns out Edward is playing a completely different game. </p> <p>And he won't stop until he's ruined me. </p> <p><b><i>Slay Two: Ruin</i></b><b> is the second book in the Slay Quartet. </b><b><i>Slay One: Rivalry</i></b><b> should be heard first.</b></p>"; 
